==== Usage notes ====
The comparative is {{m|pl|wolniejszy}} for the "slow" sense, while for the "liberty" sense the comparative is {{m|pl|[[bardziej]] wolny}}. Similarly, the corresponding adverb {{m|pl|wolno}} is usually reserved for the "slow" sense, while the "freely" sense is expressed as {{m|pl|[[w]] [[sposób]] wolny}}.

